sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Codex as codex app-server
    participant Provider as provider-domain overlay
    participant Daemon as core-daemon
    participant Swift as Swift transcript model

    Codex-->>Provider: item/commandExecution/terminalInteraction
    Note over Codex,Provider: raw stdin/control payload
    Provider->>Provider: attach terminalStdin to existing command item
    Provider-->>Daemon: streamed transcript snapshot
    Daemon-->>Swift: codex_transcript_stream_event
    Swift->>Swift: render secondary marker\nstdin raw "\\n"

    Swift->>Daemon: codex-read-transcript
    Daemon->>Provider: thread/read
    Provider-->>Daemon: ordinary snapshot without terminalStdin
    Daemon-->>Swift: readback transcript
    Note over Swift: live-only passthrough\nno persistence claim
